1.
Scope of and updates to this User Privacy Notice
Being the trusted global marketplace for insights, services and transaction solutions for commercial assets and vehicles starts with RB Global’s unrivaled commitment to customer service.  As part of that commitment, we respect the privacy of our customers and users.  Whether we are helping to appraise, sell, inspect, buy, refurbish, transport or finance your commercial assets and vehicles around the world, we are guided by our desire to meet your needs in a convenient, fair and transparent manner – and that includes making sure you understand how we handle personal information and what corresponding rights are available to you.  This Privacy Notice applies equally to our digital handling of your information as it does to our offline collection and handling.
RB Global is a global organization with companies located around the world that operate our insights, service offerings, and multi-channel solutions for buying and selling.
See a complete listing of our family of brands
.
This User Privacy Notice (“Notice” or “Privacy Notice”) applies to rbglobal.com and other RB Global brand websites, services and solutions that collect information and display or link to this Privacy Notice, and that are owned and operated by a member of the RB Global group of companies.  This Privacy Notice does not apply if the website, service or solution does not display or link to it or where the website, service or solution makes its own privacy notice available as follows:
Insurance Auto Auctions –
US
|
